&lt;p&gt;FOUNDRY HEALTHCARE LEWES is a Primary Care Network of merged NHS GP Practices looking after the residents of Lewes and the surrounding villages.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking to recruit a skilled Data Analyst to join our Team. You will be responsible for analysing, interpreting and presenting information to support performance management, service development, operational management and patient care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will provide data quality support to the division. They will be providing expertise and advice to staff at all levels which will require excellent interpersonal skills. They will also be organised and able to manage workload to meet tight deadlines.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An understanding and experience of using SystmOne will be advantageous.&lt;/p&gt;
